# Foundry Licensing

This repository contains components under different licenses:

## @inixiative/foundry-core — MIT License

The core engine primitives (context layers, agents, middleware, signals, thread,
harness, tracing, hooks, and lightweight adapters) are licensed under the MIT
License. See [LICENSE-MIT](./LICENSE-MIT) for the full text.

**Scope:** `packages/core/`

## @inixiative/foundry — Business Source License 1.1

The opinionated framework (compaction strategies, built-in hooks, session
management, planner, herald, reactive middleware, LLM providers, viewer
dashboard, logger, tunnel, and heavy-infra adapters) is licensed under the
Business Source License 1.1. You may use, copy, and modify this code freely for
any purpose **except** production commercial use. The BSL automatically converts
to MIT on the Change Date.

See [LICENSE-BSL](./LICENSE-BSL) for the full text.

**Scope:** `packages/foundry/`

## Foundry Oracle — Proprietary

The Oracle scoring service is proprietary and distributed separately under
commercial terms. It is not included in this repository.
